data.description: Check out this move-in ready home in the sought-after Colony Pointe community in Piedmont. This home has so much charm and you will see it as soon as you walk into the spacious and cozy living room area with brick fireplace and large windows that bring in tons of natural light. It's such an amazing space to spend time with your loved ones. The open and spacious kitchen has tons of storage with plenty of cabinets, tons of countertop space, a pantry, and all the amenities you can expect to find such as built-in microwave, range/oven, dishwasher, and stainless double-sink with a new modern faucet and garbage disposal. The spacious master bedroom features tall windows that provides tons of natural light, 10ft ceiling, and en suite with plenty of countertop space, stainless accents, and separate tiled shower and large tub complete this amazing space. One of the best features of this home is its amazing and spacious outdoor space that features an extended patio and patio string lights that make this the perfect space to enjoy the beautiful Oklahoma weather day or night with family and friends. The home also features a newer privacy fence that wraps around this larger lot (nearly a 1/4 acre MOL) that provides tons of space for the kiddos to enjoy the playground set that stays with the home. This backyard retreat will definitely be the space where lots of great and fun memories will be made. This home has so much character and is definitely a must see! Buyers are to verify all MLS information including schools.
